{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753170/extras/StorePage_Art01_0000_Compress01.png?t=1729376590\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">-The Background</h2> In this post apocalyptic land,There are Zombies,Survivors,and other Strange Phenomenon no one can explain.Basically <strong>no where is safe</strong> in this land except for inside <strong>SafetyHouse</strong> ,made by large Corporations.<br>Lucas is one of those Survivors,who has no friends.Can he has to be careful to Survive in this land.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753170/extras/StorePage_Gif_seq_1.gif?t=1729376590\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">-Game Features</h2>Facing Zombie,and 4 Walls is a single-Player<strong> 3rd person Shooter Zombie Survival Game</strong>.<br><strong>Rule #1</strong>:<br>Stay inside SafetyHouse before 12:00 pm.<br><strong>Rule #2</strong>:<br>Don\u2019t stay in a SafetyHouse that pass it\u2019s Best-before date.<br><strong>Rule #3</strong>:<br>Watch your Step!<br><br>In Game,Player has to Find a Safety House and Live while Dealing with Zombies,Strangers,or other Phenomenons.Player need to Go Around the Land,Searching SafetyHouse,Water and Food,Collect Metals and Wood,Fixing Generators and Lightbolts.Without being Defeated by<strong> Zombies ,or Psychopath Survivors</strong>.<br>The main goal is to<strong> Stay alive as long as Player can be</strong> in The Zombie apocalyptic World,by Following those basic Survival Rules above.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753170/extras/StorePage_Gif_seq_2.gif?t=1729376590\" /><br><br>If Player survive a new day,he will find himself and His house located in Different Location,He has to Explorde nearby Area and Find new House if needed.<br>Good Luck.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/275